  <version>SUSE Rancher Prime: OS Manager (Elemental)</version>
  <descriptions treatment="append">
    <desc lang="en-us">
        <p>
          SUSE Rancher Prime: OS Manager is a software stack enabling
          centralized, full cloud-native OS management with Kubernetes.
        </p>
        <p>
          The SUSE Rancher Prime: OS Manager Operator and the Rancher System
          Agent enable SUSE Rancher Prime to fully control SUSE Rancher Prime OS
          Manager clusters, from the installation and management of the OS on
          the Nodes to the provisioning of new K3s or RKE2 clusters in a
          centralized way.
        </p>
      </desc>
  </descriptions>
